<node id="DIVIDEND DISTRIBUTION">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">A payment made by the company to shareholders, declared in July 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;Dividend distribution involves sharing a portion of profits with shareholders as payments.&lt;SEP&gt;In January 2021, Acme Government Solutions distributed $5 million of dividends to its shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;Noted in the text as a dividend distribution event boosting shareholder returns and reflecting strong financial performance.</data>
