<node id="DEBT RESTRUCTURING">
  <data key="d0">EVENT</data>
  <data key="d1">Debt restructuring is a process where terms of existing debt are altered to make future payments more manageable.&lt;SEP&gt;Debt restructuring undertaken by Acme Government Solutions to reduce liabilities and financial costs.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of optimizing capital structure and reducing liabilities undertaken in July 2019.&lt;SEP&gt;The process of reducing EcoGuard Solutions' liabilities by $15 million in September 2019.</data>
