<node id="SHAREHOLDER EQUITY">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">Shareholder equity represents the residual claim on assets after liabilities have been settled, indicating ownership value.&lt;SEP&gt;Shareholder equity represents the residual interest in the assets of an entity after deducting liabilities. It is a key indicator of a company's financial health.&lt;SEP&gt;The residual claim on assets of a company after deducting liabilities, representing the owners' stake in the business.&lt;SEP&gt;Total amount of equity belonging to shareholders at the end of the accounting period.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fe8b781f5104d8951c214db986673a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b0d687803926f0eee439977727ffdd3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83e808b8711f18dda66b0fc1c4ad9351&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68444fef2d7d80e94081c3a494232fb5</data>
