</node>
<node id="$300 MILLION">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">The total amount of debts owed by Entertainment Enterprises Inc. at the end of the accounting period.&lt;SEP&gt;The total shareholder equity for Acme Government Solutions amounted to $300 million, driven by net profit and dividends.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-2ea080a4bbb33a9c3cb4bdf2f4855ddf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83e808b8711f18dda66b0fc1c4ad9351</data>
</node>
<node id="CASH FLOW">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Cash flow measures the amount of cash generated or used in operating activities over a specific period.&lt;SEP&gt;Cash flow represents the net amount of cash and cash equivalents being transferred into or out of a company.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-83e808b8711f18dda66b0fc1c4ad9351&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68444fef2d7d80e94081c3a494232fb5</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}]</data>
</node>
<node id="NET PROFIT">
  <data key="d0">METRIC</data>
  <data key="d1">Net profit is the amount remaining after all expenses have been deducted from total revenue.&lt;SEP&gt;The amount earned by Acme Government Solutions from its operations after accounting for expenses and taxes.&lt;SEP&gt;The profit remaining after all expenses, including taxes and interest, have been deducted from total revenue.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1b0d687803926f0eee439977727ffdd3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-83e808b8711f18dda66b0fc1c4ad9351&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68444fef2d7d80e94081c3a494232fb5</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 17}]</data>
</node>
<node id="RETURN ON EQUITY">
  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">A financial metric representing the profitability and efficiency of a company's equity.&lt;SEP&gt;A ratio reflecting operational efficiency based on net profit and shareholder equity.&lt;SEP&gt;The return on equity for the company is 12%, indicating satisfactory returns for shareholders.</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-fe8b781f5104d8951c214db986673a3e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b66c40857191417b60e60f565f026a50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-635dd634ef004a57e780cede9f63dab2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 16}]</data>
</node>
<node id="OPERATIONAL EFFICIENCY">
